{"tid":1280394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄：示威者衝擊立法會是集體自毀","createTime":"2019-07-03T03:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T10:41:10.000Z","uid":212626,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97cf87ae45697ab8914872f4d30bd55480f3b0dd","tid":1280394,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"工黨立法會議員張超雄出席電台節目時表示，示威者前日闖入立法會是針對權力的象徵作出破壞，<span style=\"color: red;\">並非傷害他人，是下一代在絕望中做出的行為</span>。他指出，示威者<span style=\"color: red;\">並非出於一時衝動，而是經詳細考慮才行動</span>，部分人甚至將3名示威者的輕生，怪責在自己身上，決定<span style=\"color: red;\">以死相搏</span>，形容示威者是<span style=\"color: red;\">集體自毀</span>。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄又指出，民主派立法會議員當日心情矛盾，與抗爭者有同樣的訴求，但當時立法會並無開會，亦非正審議修訂《逃犯條例》，不認為他們的方法能夠達到目標，因此議員決定抵擋示威者。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉表示，示威者的抗爭對象是政府，經歷過百萬人上街遊行、警方開槍、有人失去性命，但政府仍然無動於衷，令示威者感到絕望，而政府堅持要舉行七一升旗禮、慶祝回歸22周年，示威者未能到場表達訴求，是觸發及後衝擊立法會事件的主因。他認為，多名市民輕生，是港人的悲劇，但政府仍大肆舉行喜慶酒會是不恰當，示威者無意傷他人，亦有保護文物，不認同示威者是暴力，也並非暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉又稱，問題自多年前已經開始累積，包括人大8.31決定扼殺普選的可能，以及政府剝奪部分人的參與權等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2181227/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2181227%2F&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=c4bf1677\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2181227/</a>"},{"pid":"e05a0b81d7bbe2f6e667df35ad5b046472946099","tid":1280394,"uid":21545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:17:42.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3eba82530a063d96e5bbc9617b89fd3b911d5b","tid":1280394,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e05a0b81d7bbe2f6e667df35ad5b046472946099","tid":1280394,"uid":21545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:17:42.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"管吓你老豆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93685c061803df7c4eb9e4e15537c6a89d7091e3","tid":1280394,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb01f9105b19f2b0c0e456e631f42d8f9e09412","tid":1280394,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e05a0b81d7bbe2f6e667df35ad5b046472946099","tid":1280394,"uid":21545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:17:42.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"南亞大軍準備好未"},{"pid":"72bbc931cf87d7ee9b9ccdc807c875ed229bb395","tid":1280394,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"總算講護d人話"},{"pid":"f8991f34e552be6e2e0e0d4d585cf8bbc7e65f67","tid":1280394,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cbb7e23d47d87d6ea8b0b0b2b2a3cdacff6d87","tid":1280394,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}